message.body: Hey Gabi sorry this is last minute but I can't make it today I'm at my grandparents working. Are you going to be in the studio on Monday?
No worries, make sure you let Matt at the store know. I wont be there monday at 530 this week, but we can schedule a make up. Are you free thursday?
I can let you know soon. I need to check with hannaford. Ill let you know ASAP!
